=head1 DESCRIPTION

Text extraction encountered one or more page-level errors in the input
document.

The C<ErrorCode> contains one of the following values:

=over

=item *

TEXTRACT_BAD_PAGE - Amazon Textract cannot read the page. For more
information about page limits in Amazon Textract, see Page Quotas in
Amazon Textract
(https://docs.aws.amazon.com/textract/latest/dg/limits-document.html).

=item *

TEXTRACT_PROVISIONED_THROUGHPUT_EXCEEDED - The number of requests
exceeded your throughput limit. For more information about throughput
quotas in Amazon Textract, see Default quotas in Amazon Textract
(https://docs.aws.amazon.com/textract/latest/dg/limits-quotas-explained.html).

=item *

PAGE_CHARACTERS_EXCEEDED - Too many text characters on the page (10,000
characters maximum).

=item *

PAGE_SIZE_EXCEEDED - The maximum page size is 10 MB.

=item *

INTERNAL_SERVER_ERROR - The request encountered a service issue. Try
the API request again.

=back


=head1 ATTRIBUTES


=head2 ErrorCode => Str

Error code for the cause of the error.


=head2 ErrorMessage => Str

Text message explaining the reason for the error.


=head2 Page => Int

Page number where the error occurred.



